      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "10-86.2",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t10-86.2-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t10-86.2-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "differential quotient of kerma (<<t10-86.1>>) with respect to time (<<iso80000-3>>):\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\ndot K = (\"d\"K)/(\"d\"t)\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\n1 \"unitsml(Gy/s)\" = 1 \"unitsml(W/kg)\"\n++++\n\nSee the Remarks for <<t10-81.1>>.\n\nIn report 85a of the ICRU a definition with an equivalent meaning is given as:\n\nThe kerma rate, stem:[dot K], is the quotient of stem:[\"d\"K] by stem:[\"d\"t], where stem:[\"d\"K] is the increment of kerma in the time interval stem:[\"d\"t]:\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\ndot K = (\"d\"K)/(\"d\"t).\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-Gy/s"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-W/kg"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-m^2*s^(-3)"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-10"
      }
    }
  ]
